    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Prints made by collagraph printing, using a printing surface created by gluing objects to a support; can be relief or intaglio, and is often a hybrid of the two in that ink can be held and printed from recesses or the surface of the matrix.</Note_Text>
